  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1244">
<l>kaṇṇuṅ koḷaccēṟi neñcē ~ivaiyeṉṉait </l>
<l> tiṉṉu mavarkāṇa luṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul! take my eyes also with you, (if not), these would eat me up (in their desire) to see him.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
